{"tid":1576391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肯肯定港共黑狗係唔會畀黨鐵公開831 cctv","createTime":"2019-09-17T08:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T12:35:18.000Z","uid":27451,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"08bece295659935ecd40887204d1b7827975c7af","tid":1576391,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:33:28.000Z","msg":"如果黑狗真係無打死示威者，一早攞條片出黎證明自己清白啦，到今日都死唔放CCTV.<br />\n<br />\n如果黑狗真係有打死示威者或打到失去知覺，如果真係公報出黎，整個港共政權還可以生存? 依家係港共政權生死存亡之時，根本係無可能會放條cctv出黎。<br />\n<br />\n至於話用法律手段要黨鐵送cctv出黎?<br />\n港共有好多方法可以令條片消失包括好多意外會發生架。"},{"pid":"a05b01b3b54a716e372f0a64551708846cc81722","tid":1576391,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"c22bfee523c795b62d958b227f8d269838c25242","tid":1576391,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:00:08.000Z","msg":"好黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411dc2f532f81418928921928b7ef8b260cadc64","tid":1576391,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df050357d216f91001607054887bf2538a072f3","tid":1576391,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2